; --- Aethersailor 代理补丁（仅兜底用，不越权）---
ruleset=🚀 手动选择,clash-domain:https://testingcf.jsdelivr.net/gh/Aethersailor/Custom_OpenClash_Rules@main/rule/Custom_Proxy_Domain.yaml,28800
